image_analysis.description: A photograph of a storage or utility room. In the foreground, there are several vacuum cleaners, including two Dyson cordless models mounted on the wall and a red upright vacuum. A gray hand truck (dolly) is positioned in the center. In the background, there is a hallway leading to a row of white lockers. To the right, a white countertop and sink are partially visible. The floor is covered in dark carpeting.
image_analysis.layout: Interior room shot with equipment in the foreground and a hallway with lockers in the background.
